movie_title: Star Wars: Episode I - The Phantom Menace
title: If you understand this move as the retelling of classic myth, it works quite well.
review: If you understand this move as the retelling of classic myth, it works quite well.No, the characters aren't fully fleshed out.  Yes, the story is implausible in parts.  But that's what myth is like.  Understood, and appreciated, as myth, this is an entertaining and enjoyable piece of fluff.
